\v 22 Eebbi Mootii Waan Maraa durummaa kenna; 
\q2 inni rakkinna isi'itti hin dabalu. 
\q1  
\v 23 Nami gowwaan waan hantuu hujiisatti gammada; 
\q2 nami hubantii qabu ammoo 
\q2 qarumma'atti gammada. 
\q1  
\v 24 Nama hamaa waan inni guddoo sodaatutti itti dhufa; 
\q2 nama balchaa ammoo 
\q2 waan inni guddoo halchutti isaaf kennama. 
