\v 29 Karaan Mootii Waan Maraa 
\q2 worra balcha'aaf gollaa jaddu'u; 
\q2 worra hantuu hujuuf ammoo badi'i. 
\q1  
\v 30 Worri balchaan ijjumaa hin munyuuqu; 
\q2 worri hamaan ammoo lafa irratti hin hafu. 
\q1  
\v 31 Afaan worra balcha'aa qarummaa dubbata; 
\q2 arrabi dubbii micciiru ammoo hin murama. 
\q1  
\v 32 Afaan worra balcha'aa dubbii toltu beeka; 
\q2 afaan worra hama'aa ammoo micciiriisa qofa beeka. 
