\v 22 Mootiin Waan Maraa afaan dhara dubbatu jibba; 
\q2 namoota dhugaammeyyi'itti ammoo hin gammada. 
\q1  
\v 23 Nami qalbeeffataan beekkumsa ifii dhoffata; 
\q2 namooti gowwaan ammoo 
\q2 gowwummaa ifii mudhifatan. 
